{"tid":446038,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張家輝案今早提堂 准以一萬港元保釋","createTime":"2017-10-24T03:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T07:30:26.000Z","uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1d42e979e5ed4c913c6ca4da0676d1656d96dad4","tid":446038,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T03:02:38.000Z","msg":"警長涉藉公職脅享免費按摩　待轉區院押後訊 (10:22)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=KHW6nftp2oq6oQc8USE1U7DFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=5e2fa58f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】廉政公署早前落案起訴一名警長，涉嫌藉公職作出不當行為，涉案警長張家輝被控兩項藉公職作出不當行為罪名，案件今(24日)在九龍城裁判法院提堂，被告毋須答辯，控方申請將案件押後至下月14日，等候轉介往區域法院答辯的文件，期間被告准以一萬港元保釋，但不得騷擾控方證人。<br />\n<br />\n涉案警長<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>張家輝</strong></span>，現年50歲，隸屬九龍城分區雜項調查小隊，其中一項職責是就九龍城區內的按摩院進行巡查及放蛇行動。而他被控兩項罪名，包括涉嫌接受一間按摩院免費按摩服務而向按摩院女主管通風報信，告知她警方即將進行的行動，以及向另一間按摩院的女東主施壓，迫使她以較低價錢向一名女商人出售其按摩院。"},{"pid":"f6ff015df56858f9c05641d074338fe7235fc776","tid":446038,"uid":38820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T03:17:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/24/111732_704b27084030f0e97ce3ce3e5953e9e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F24%2F111732_704b27084030f0e97ce3ce3e5953e9e5.jpg&h=bf81e588&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efbe6a02fdbf638ab00d5a57aadae9ced017b859","tid":446038,"uid":44333,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T03:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i1.sinaimg.cn/dy/slidenews/4_img/2014_03/704_1215600_792317.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.sinaimg.cn%2Fdy%2Fslidenews%2F4_img%2F2014_03%2F704_1215600_792317.jpg&h=f8a5ff27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a5b8ebe4adc613ebd936012df3a08d689d6d9fa","tid":446038,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T05:37:25.000Z","msg":"上面2張圖<i